---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Pressly">
	<div class="relative min-h-screen bg-[#F8FAFC] selection:bg-primary/20 selection:text-primary pb-32">
		<!-- Minimalist Hero -->
		<div class="relative pt-32 pb-24 overflow-hidden flex flex-col items-center text-center px-6">
			<!-- Subtle mesh background -->
			<div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none z-0 flex items-center justify-center">
				<div class="w-[800px] h-[800px] bg-gradient-to-tr from-blue-100/40 via-primary/5 to-cyan-100/40 rounded-full blur-[100px] opacity-70"></div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="relative z-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<span class="inline-block py-1 px-3 rounded-full bg-white border border-slate-200 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-slate-500 uppercase mb-6 animate-fade-in-up">Legal</span>
				<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-display font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight mb-6 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
					Your privacy,<br/>
					<span class="text-primary">protected.</span>
				</h1>
				<p class="text-xl text-slate-500 font-medium animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
					We believe in radical transparency. Here's exactly how we handle your data.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Main Document Container -->
		<div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
			<div class="bg-white rounded-[2rem] p-8 md:p-16 lg:p-20 shadow-[0_20px_60px_-15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] border border-slate-100/50 animate-fade-in-up mb-20" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
				
				<div class="flex items-center justify-between pb-8 border-b border-slate-100 mb-12">
					<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Effective Date</p>
					<p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 bg-slate-100 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full">June 2026</p>
				</div>

				<div class="space-y-16 text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-sans">
					
					<!-- Section 1 -->
					<section>
						<h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">1. The short version</h2>
						<p class="mb-4">
							At Pressly, we only collect the data we absolutely need to provide you with an exceptional laundry experience. We don't sell your data to advertisers, and we never will.
						</p>
						<p>
							This policy outlines the specifics of what we collect, why we collect it, and the rigorous security measures we employ to keep it safe.
						</p>
					</section>

					<!-- Section 2 -->
					<section>
						<h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">2. Information we collect</h2>
						<p class="mb-6">
							To facilitate seamless pickups, drop-offs, and payments, we require specific data points. We categorize this into information you provide directly and information we collect automatically.
						</p>
						
						<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-8">
							<div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
								<div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-white shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-4">
									<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M19 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H9a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
								</div>
								<h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Account Data</h3>
								<p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Name, email, phone number, and physical address for coordinating laundry pickups and deliveries.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
								<div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-white shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-4">
									<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="5" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><line x1="2" y1="10" x2="22" y2="10"/></svg>
								</div>
								<h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Payment Data</h3>
								<p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Processed securely via our payment partners. We never store your full credit card details on our servers.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</section>

					<!-- Section 3 -->
					<section>
						<h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">3. How your data is used</h2>
						<p class="mb-4">
							Your data is strictly used to fulfill the services you request from Pressly. This includes:
						</p>
						<ul class="space-y-4 mt-6">
							<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
								<div class="mt-1 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
									<div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>
								</div>
								<span>Connecting you with the best local laundry vendors.</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
								<div class="mt-1 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
									<div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>
								</div>
								<span>Providing real-time tracking for your orders.</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
								<div class="mt-1 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
									<div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>
								</div>
								<span>Sending transactional updates via email and push notifications.</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</section>

					<!-- Section 4 -->
					<section>
						<h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">4. Enterprise-grade security</h2>
						<p>
							We treat your personal information with the utmost care. All data transmitted between your device and our servers is encrypted using industry-standard TLS. Data at rest is secured via AES-256 encryption. Access to production databases is strictly limited to authorized personnel and is logged comprehensively.
						</p>
					</section>
					
					<!-- Section 5 -->
					<section class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 p-8 md:p-10 rounded-3xl mt-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-6">
						<div>
							<h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 tracking-tight">Have questions?</h2>
							<p class="text-slate-500 max-w-xl">
								If you have any questions or concerns about how your data is handled, our Data Protection Officer is ready to help.
							</p>
						</div>
						<a href="mailto:privacy@pressly.app" class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center gap-2 bg-slate-900 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-slate-800 transition-colors">
							Email Privacy Team
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
						</a>
					</section>

				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
